Pour un acteur donné en paramètre, afficher les événements (valeurs de la table events) qui y font référence (dans les derniers 6 mois).

paragraphs.text:
%python
from cassandra.cluster import Cluster
from cassandra.query import SimpleStatement
from cassandra.auth import PlainTextAuthProvider
import pandas as pd
import functools, operator
import folium
from datetime import datetime, timedelta
from cassandra import ConsistencyLevel

def pandas_factory(colnames, rows):
    return pd.DataFrame(rows, columns=colnames)
#'18.215.185.37','3.91.34.21','18.232.144.176'
cluster = Cluster(
    contact_points=['18.215.185.37','3.91.34.21','18.232.144.176'], 
    auth_provider = PlainTextAuthProvider(username='cassandra', password='cassandra')
)
session = cluster.connect()
bquorum = True
session.set_keyspace('gdelt')
session.row_factory = pandas_factory
session.default_fetch_size = 10000000 #needed for large queries, otherwise driver will do pagination. Default is 50000.

%python
#col1 = z.select("Type d'acteur", )
strTypeAct="1"
strReqList = """select distinct a_full_name as "actor name" from gdelt.requete2b"""
##ss = SimpleStatement(strReqList, consistency_level=ConsistencyLevel.QUORUM)
if bquorum == True:
    ss = SimpleStatement(strReqList, consistency_level=ConsistencyLevel.QUORUM)
    rows = session.execute(ss,timeout=400)
else : 
    rows = session.execute(strReqList)
list = session.execute(strReqList)
dflist = list._current_rows.sort_values(by="actor name")
#z.show(dflist)
strLstAct = str(functools.reduce(lambda x, y:    x + """<option value=\"""" + y  + """\"> """ , dflist.values).flatten())
strLstAct = strLstAct[19:]
z.z.angularBind("actors", strLstAct)

%python
def myfdate(param):
    sdt = str(datetime(int(param[:4]), int(param[5:7]), int(param[8:10]), 23, 0)+  timedelta(hours=1))
    return (sdt[:4]+sdt[5:7]+sdt[8:10])
strActeur = z.z.angular("actorname")
z.z.angularBind( "actor", strActeur )
nTop = 100
#print(z.z.angular("actorname"))
#print(z.z.angular("topN"))
if z.z.angular("topN") != None:
    nTop = int(z.z.angular("topN"))
z.z.angularBind( "nntop", nTop )

#print(z.z.angular("newDate"))
#print(z.z.angular("fromDate"))
#print(myfdate(z.z.angular("fromDate")))
#print(z.z.angular("toDate"))
nStartDate = myfdate(z.z.angular("fromDate"))
nEndtDate =  myfdate(z.z.angular("toDate"))

#print(nStartDate)

strReq = """select a_full_name as "actor", a_type as "type of actor", e_action as action, e_quad_class as "type of action", r_sens as way, 
            a2_name as "actor linked", a2_type as "type of actor linked", e_country_label as place, e_sql_date as when, e_num_mentions as importance,a_lat,a_long, a2_lat,a2_long, e_lat,e_long, a_country_code, a_country, a_ethnic, a_group, a_religion, e_goldsteinScale as goldtein, eventglobalid as eventglobalid  
            from requete2b WHERE a_full_name='""" + strActeur + """' AND e_sql_date >= """ + str(nStartDate) + " AND e_sql_date <= """ + str(nEndtDate) 
##ss = SimpleStatement(strReq, consistency_level=ConsistencyLevel.QUORUM)
if bquorum == True:
    ss = SimpleStatement(strReq, consistency_level=ConsistencyLevel.QUORUM)
    rows = session.execute(ss)
else : 
    rows = session.execute(strReq)
#print(strReq)
a_title=""
a_title2=""
df = rows._current_rows
if (df.shape[0]> 0):
    a_title = df['actor'].loc[0]
    a_country = df['a_country'].loc[0]
    a_group = df['a_group'].loc[0]
    a_ethnic = df['a_ethnic'].loc[0]
    a_religion = df['a_religion'].loc[0]
    a_title2 = ""
    if a_country != '' : a_title2 = a_title2 + "country : %s\n" % (a_country)
    if a_group != '' : a_title2 = a_title2 + "known group : %s\n" % (a_group)
    if a_ethnic != '' : a_title2 = a_title2 + "ethnic : %s\n" % (a_ethnic)
    if a_religion != '' : a_title2 = a_title2 + "religion : %s\n" % (a_religion)
else:
    a_title = "Actor not found"
z.z.angularBind( "title", a_title )
z.z.angularBind( "title2", a_title2 )
dfdisp = df[["actor","action", "type of action", "way", "actor linked","type of actor linked","place", "when", "importance"]].sort_values(by="importance",ascending=False)
z.show(dfdisp.head(nTop))
